	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Apr 4th 2:30 PM 2003</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.90]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Your CCS is the best piece of armor you have. upgrade everything else first.<br><br>Start by scrapping the serp bracers, for acrylia reinforced, or if money is a problem, bracers of erollis and hardened kodiak bracer.<br><br>Get gold/plat/or velium fire wedding rings to replace the bandit rings.<br><br>Those earrings you're wearing have no stats. sell them and get orc fang earrings.<br><br>Upgrade the ulaks. Personally, I like fighting batons, but Cane of the Tranquil is nice also.<br><br>Get spider fur for neck, back, and waist.<br><br>Then start saving for haste item. I like silver chitin handwraps for monks.<br><br>Once you have upgraded most of your other gear, THEN worry about the robe. Its pretty decent!<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Apr&nbsp;&nbsp;4 13:56:14 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
